reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater fits nicely, with one mentioning it pairs perfectly with skinny jeans, and appreciate its subtle design on the sleeves. Customers like the color options, with one highlighting its Fall pumpkin tone.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality beautiful color.
items.body: Beautiful color! I got the L the fit was great. Soft fabric not itchy at all. Very happy with the quality and design! Read more
items.author: Elaine Segarra

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome Sweater!
items.body: I have purchased 4 of these sweaters, the colors are very vibrant and they are very soft. They are true to size, comfortable to wear with any outfit you choose. The price is affordable! It’s just one of my favorite sweaters to wear! I recommend them to anyone who wants a great sweater for the winter or whenever needed!!! Thank you! Read more
items.author: Snooks

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute, a lil smaller than a regular medium.
items.body: Cute, a lil smaller than a regular medium. The interior is super soft and not itchy. Read more
items.author: Angey

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars cute and comfy
items.body: Love these sweaters, I bought them in 4 colors. It's nice and cozy and cute. I wash them and hang dry them (I'm not sure if it's necessary but it feels safer haha) I think they're true to size. Read more
items.author: Erika

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars One for the winters..
items.body: I was skeptical but nice sweater! Fabric feels good. Not cheap. I got a medium. I’m about 145 - 5’6 and it fits nice. Color is good. No complaints. Pleased with this sweater. Good buy for your wardrobe. Read more
items.author: Melinda Whitmore

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Great as long as you do not put through dryer
items.body: Straight out of the package: AMAZING. It is a slightly oversized fit. Really soft, adorable. Quality feel. Made the mistake of PUTTING IT THROUGH THE DRYER and IT SHRUNK TO BE TOO SHORT. Material held up fine, no pilling, snags etc. But craaazy amount of shrinkage.. I am 5’5 150lbs. So, if I were to order again I would get an XL to maintain oversized fit after washing/drying. Or, remember to air dry this item and order your normal size. Read more
items.author: AV

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute overall
items.body: This was cute. I would definitely size down as it is a bit oversized. I like the soft fabric and that it’s not too heavy- more on the thinner side. You’ll need a jacket/coat in the winter! The quality for the price is on par. I am a little afraid to wash it because the fabric isn’t super high quality and I think it might pill. Read more
items.author: JNichole

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful fall sweater
items.body: This is a great sweater. It is light weight to wear in the fall but heavy enough to wear in an office during winter. Loved the color. The sweater is as pictured and true to size Read more
items.author: Mark

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Wine, Greypink, Royalblue, Deeporange, Black, Camel, Coffee, Dustyblue, Oatmeal, Taro, Armygreen, Red, Navy, Khaki. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
